Source: PrisaThe annual Prism Awards is the official public relations and communications awards programme of the Public Relations Institute of Southern Africa (Prisa), the only SAQA recognised professional body for the industry, celebrating exceptional performance in public relations campaigns. The Prism Awards judges are made up of a panel of 67 judges alongside 10 young judges selected as part of the Prisms Young Voices (PYV) mentorship and peer-to-peer training initiative.Source: Prisa